txt.en: You have defeated many foes at Dâr Grazadh.
Many foes can be found in Dâr Grazadh.\n\nYou should defeat any foes you find.
You have defeated many of the Dead at Dâr Grazadh. The Rangers of Ithilien will be pleased with your efforts.

Dâr Grazadh, once a great guild-hall of Minas Ithil, is now a hall of rot that houses the Dead. Many terrible risen creations wander its halls and should be defeated for the safety of all those who must brave the Dead City.
Many foes can be found in Dâr Grazadh.\n\nYou should defeat any foes you find.
Dâr Grazadh, once a great guild-hall of Minas Ithil, is now a hall of rot that houses the Dead in their many forms.
